<div class="notification-content">
    <h2>ðŸ”§ Vehicle Marked as Parted Out</h2>

    <div class="vehicle-details">
        <h3>{{vehicle.make}} {{vehicle.model}} ({{vehicle.year}})</h3>

        <div class="vehicle-info">
            <p><strong>VIN:</strong> {{vehicle.vin}</p>
            <p><strong>Status:</strong> <span class="status-parted-out">Parted Out</span></p>
            <p><strong>Updated:</strong> {{formatDate vehicle.updatedAt}}</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="status-explanation">
        <p><strong>What this means:</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li>The vehicle has been marked as parted out</li>
            <li>Parts from this vehicle are now available for sale</li>
            <li>Profit tracking will be enabled for parts sales</li>
            <li>The vehicle will no longer appear in intact inventory</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="user-info">
        <p><strong>Updated by:</strong> {{updatedBy.fullName}} ({{updatedBy.email}})</p>
    </div>

    <div class="action-buttons">
        <a href="{{vehicleUrl}}" class="btn btn-primary">View Vehicle Details</a>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>This notification was sent to all administrators and managers.</p>
        <p>You can track parts sales and profitability for this vehicle through the admin panel.</p>
    </div>
</div>